messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
I can help with that if you can share your current latitude and longitude. Could you please provide your coordinates (latitude and longitude)?
I don't have them right now.

I’m not able to determine your location without some form of input. If you’re able to share your current latitude and longitude, or an approximate address/city, I can help look up where you are. Let me know what you can provide!
I can't provide my location. Maybe you can figure it out on your end?

I’m sorry, but I don’t have any way to pinpoint your whereabouts without some form of location data from you—whether that’s GPS coordinates, an IP-based lookup (which you’d have to authorize), or even a rough address or landmark. If you can share any of those, I’d be happy to help identify where you are.
